00073 char* TagSet::convertCodeToTagString(unsigned int code)
00074 {
00075         unsigned short int scode = (unsigned short int)( code & 0x0000ffff );
00076         unsigned short int pos=0;
00077 
00078         if (scode)
00079         {
00080                 pos = scode % HASHING_DIV_VALUE;
00081 
00082                 if (code == smallAGroupTags[pos].code) return smallAGroupTags[pos].tag;
00083                 else if (code == smallBGroupTags[pos].code) return smallBGroupTags[pos].tag;
00084         }
00085         else
00086         {
00087                 scode = (unsigned short int)(code >> 16);
00088 
00089                 pos = scode % HASHING_DIV_VALUE;
00090 
00091                 if (code == largeGroupTags[pos].code) return largeGroupTags[pos].tag;
00092         }
00093 
00094         return "";
00095 }
